                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        851,
                                        2108,
                                        1131
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Datasets. Experiments are performed on benchmark datasets with diverse mathematical problems, including MMLU [Hendrycks et al. (2021a), SVAMP Patel et al. (2021), GSM8K [Cobbe et al. (2021), AQuA [Ling et al. (2017) and MATH Hendrycks et al. (2021b). Besides, we include a challenging mathematical reasoning task, Game of 24 Yao et al. (2024), where the goal is to use four numbers and basic arithmetic operations (addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division) to obtain 24 in 1 equation. Thus, the solution includes 3 intermediate steps."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 2
                },
                {
