                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " thought structures, each being a weighted binary tree because this tends to achieve optimal results. Besides, for those benchmark datasets, we set the depth of the tree to be 5 while the corresponding depth in Game of 24 is 3. BoT+CoT means our simple prompt includes 5 examples from CoT [Wei et al. (2022). In the ablation study, when no experience is accumulated in BoT, 8 examples of CoT will be provided in the prompt."
